issues.description: Profile "Profile_1" has one or more connections configured with Use-BIOS boot settings. OneView does not support profile connections configured with a mixture of Use-BIOS and other boot settings.
issues.recommendation: The Virtual Connect Use-BIOS boot setting will be automatically changed to not bootable in OneView.

issues.description: Profile "Profile_1" FCoE connection 1 is configured for factory MAC and a factory WWN of 10:00:6C:C2:17:39:95:A1. The WWN for this connection may change after migration to OneView.
issues.recommendation: After the migration task has completed, validate the WWNs of the migrated profiles for any potential changes. If a WWN change occurred, change the SAN fabric and storage configuration to reflect the new WWNs before powering on the servers.
